Title: An Act Changing the Name of Mabalor Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibaan, Province of Batangas, to Mabalor-Catandala Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 771
An Act Changing the Name of Mabalor Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibaan, Province of Batangas, to Mabalor-Catandala Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Mabalor Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibaan, Province of Batangas, is changed to Mabalor-Catandala Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
